      "6th_edition_harpercollins_isbn_13_978_0063092464_is": ", 6th edition, HarperCollins, ISBN-13: 978-0063092464, is a major reference for the Collaborative & Proactive Solutions approach. It is especially relevant when punishments and rewards are not enough because the child is missing specific flexibility, frustration-tolerance or problem-solving skills.",
